               <div align="left">
                <font face="宋体 "><font size="3">　心不相行　　得非得同分<br /></font></font>
               </div>
               <div align="left">
                <font face="宋体 "><font size="3">　o想二定命　　相名身等<br /></font></font>
               </div>
